      <title>Metropolitan Kallistos Ware on the State of the Orthodox Church</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheIlluminedHeart/~3/zmphVi1Scwk/metropolitan_kallistos_ware_state_of_orthodox_church</link>
