      <title>100: Indian And Orthodox</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheIlluminedHeart/~3/7oUrHx5rfs0/indian_and_orthodox</link>
     <guid isPermaLink="false">http://ancientfaith.com/podcasts/illuminedheart/indian_and_orthodox#3836</guid>
 <description>In this edition, host Kevin Allen speaks with Tenny Thomas, a  doctoral student at Columbia/Union Theological Seminary, and member  of the Malankara Orthodox Syrian Church, also known as the Indian  Orthodox Church, about the Indian Christian community and how Indian  Orthodox Christians relate to and evangelize in their predominantly  Hindu society.&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
