      <title>Is There A “Revolving Door” In The Orthodox Church</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheIlluminedHeart/~3/4kx_NZS9tR4/is</link>
     <guid isPermaLink="false">http://ancientfaith.com/podcasts/illuminedheart/is#2396</guid>
 <description>In this encore presentation, Kevin's guest is Dr. Brad Nassif. Are converts coming into the Orthodox churches only to leave through a “revolving door” due to a lack of spiritual nourishment? Theologian Dr. Bradley Nassif’s controversial article on the subject (“Reclaiming the Gospel”) is the subject of this frank and hard-hitting interview.&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
