      <title>Collateral Damage: Iraq’s persecuted Christians</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheIlluminedHeart/~3/xBVqcXqp0g0/collateral_damage_iraqs_persecuted_christians</link>
     <guid isPermaLink="false">http://ancientfaith.com/podcasts/illuminedheart/collateral_damage_iraqs_persecuted_christians#1843</guid>
 <description>As many as 30%+ of Iraqi's 4.2 million displaced refugees are Christian. They are being persecuted from all sides of the conflict. Amal Morcos of IOCC recently returned from Syria and Lebanon and reports first hand on what the U.N. calls "the fastest growing refugee crisis in the world."&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
